(f) monitor and evaluate the performance of the Agency
against budgets and plans;
(g) establish and approve rules and procedures for the
appointment, discipline, termination and terms and
conditions of service of the staff of the Agency; and
(h) perform any other function conferred or imposed on the
Board by, or under, this Act.

